trans-unit.source: Represents a value tuple with 5 components.
trans-unit.target: 表示含有 5 個元件的值元組。

trans-unit.source: A value tuple is a data structure that has a specific number and sequence of values.
trans-unit.target: 值 tuple 是具有特定數量和值序列的資料結構。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ValueTuple%605> structure represents a value tuple that has five elements.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ValueTuple%605>結構代表有五個元素的值 tuple。

trans-unit.source: The value tuple types differ from the tuple types (such as <xref:System.Tuple%605>) as follows:
trans-unit.target: 與 tuple 類型不同的值 tuple 的類型 (例如<xref:System.Tuple%605>)，如下所示：

trans-unit.source: They are structures (value types) rather than classes (reference types).
trans-unit.target: 它們是結構 （實值類型），而不是類別 （參考型別）。

trans-unit.source: Members such as <xref:System.ValueTuple%605.Item1> and <xref:System.ValueTuple%605.Item2> are fields rather than properties.
trans-unit.target: 這類成員<xref:System.ValueTuple%605.Item1>和<xref:System.ValueTuple%605.Item2>欄位，而不是屬性。

trans-unit.source: Their fields are mutable rather than read-only.
trans-unit.target: 其欄位都是可變動而不是唯讀狀態。

trans-unit.source: The value tuple types provide the runtime implementation that supports [tuples in C#](~/docs/csharp/tuples.md) and struct tuples in F#.
trans-unit.target: 值 tuple 的類型提供支援的執行階段實作[C# 中的 tuple](~/docs/csharp/tuples.md)和結構在 F # 中的 tuple。

trans-unit.source: In addition to creating a <xref:System.ValueTuple%605> instance by using language syntax, you can call the <xref:System.ValueTuple.Create%2A> factory method.
trans-unit.target: 除了建立<xref:System.ValueTuple%605>執行個體所使用的語言語法，您可以呼叫<xref:System.ValueTuple.Create%2A>factory 方法。

trans-unit.source: Serialization and value tuples
trans-unit.target: 序列化和值的 tuple

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ValueTuple%605> type is not serializable in .NET Core 1.x or in the .NET Framework 4.7 and earlier versions.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ValueTuple%605>類型不是可序列化的.NET Core 1.x 或.NET Framework 4.7 和更早版本中。

trans-unit.source: In addition, .NET Standard, including .NET Standard 2.0, does not mandate serialization of <xref:System.ValueTuple%605> instances; whether or not a <xref:System.ValueTuple%605> instance is serializable depends on the individual .NET Standard implementation.
trans-unit.target: 此外，.NET 標準，包括標準的.NET 2.0，不會要求的序列化<xref:System.ValueTuple%605>執行個體; 是否<xref:System.ValueTuple%605>是可序列化的執行個體取決於個別的.NET 標準實作。

trans-unit.source: To determine whether a <xref:System.ValueTuple%605> type is serializable on a particular .NET implementation, get a <xref:System.Type> object that represents the <xref:System.ValueTuple%605> type and retrieve the value of its <xref:System.Type.IsSerializable%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 若要判斷是否<xref:System.ValueTuple%605>型別可序列化特定的.NET 實作、 取得<xref:System.Type>物件，代表<xref:System.ValueTuple%605>類型及擷取的值其<xref:System.Type.IsSerializable%2A>屬性。

trans-unit.source: For a list of serializable types in .NET Core and the .NET Framework, see [Binary Serialization](~/docs/standard/serialization/binary-serialization.md).
trans-unit.target: 如需可序列化的型別.NET Core 和.NET Framework 中的清單，請參閱[二進位序列化](~/docs/standard/serialization/binary-serialization.md)。
